OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny cloud breaking up to allow
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells, and becoming warm.
OL,7,FCloud and patchy rain spreading to the
OL,8,FIsles later in afternoon. Mainly light
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe far northwest including
OL,12,FLewis and the North Coast of Highland
OL,13,Fstaying cloudy with occasional mainly
OL,14,Flight rain this evening, becoming dry
OL,15,Fovernight. Elsewhere some good clear
OL,16,Fspells overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
