OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA generally dry bright day
OL,6,Fwith some good sunny spells and
OL,7,Fbecoming very warm. The Isles will
OL,8,Fcloud over towards evening with some
OL,9,Fmist.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fstart in west on Wednesday, burning
OL,13,Foff then some sunshine, very warm.
OL,14,FThursday bright and very warm or hot
OL,15,Fthen some thundery showers. Less warm,
OL,16,Fshowery on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
